  "bio_raw": "Afsana Anjum has eight years of experience of teaching the History of Bangladesh and World History at the University of Liberal Arts, Bangladesh. Before starting teaching she worked in the development sector for one year. She graduated from the University of Dhaka and continued on to post-graduate study there. She is now doing her Ph.D. at the same University.\nIn addition to teaching, she has been working as the coordinator of the General Education Department since 2013 and was the advisor of the ULAB Social Welfare Club from 2010 to 2012.",
